1
00:00:24,243 --> 00:00:28,011
I don't have any classes today.

2
00:00:47,430 --> 00:00:50,678
[Kim Yunghui: Let's meet up tonight
Senior: It's time to trust your abilities]

3
00:00:59,019 --> 00:01:00,507
Thank you.

4
00:01:05,712 --> 00:01:08,601
Since we both have free
time, wanna go somewhere?

5
00:01:08,602 --> 00:01:09,689
Huh?

6
00:01:09,690 --> 00:01:12,158
Let's eat first and head out.

7
00:01:20,780 --> 00:01:22,461
Do you remember what happened yesterday?

8
00:01:22,462 --> 00:01:24,462
What?

9
00:01:24,933 --> 00:01:26,709
Uh...

10
00:01:26,710 --> 00:01:28,728
Yeah

11
00:01:28,729 --> 00:01:30,728
I trust you.

12
00:01:30,729 --> 00:01:32,359
What?

13
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:35,082
I knew about Kim Jaehyun.

14
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:39,559
The day my brother died,

15
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,013
there was a strange man beside him,

16
00:01:41,014 --> 00:01:43,275
telling him it'd be okay
and pushing him forward.

17
00:01:43,276 --> 00:01:46,410
By the time I turned back
around, he was already gone

18
00:01:46,411 --> 00:01:49,508
I tried to track down that stranger,

19
00:01:49,509 --> 00:01:51,190
but I didn't even know his name,

20
00:01:51,191 --> 00:01:54,903
and there wasn't a single
trace of him anywhere.

21
00:01:56,483 --> 00:01:57,500
Then...

22
00:01:57,501 --> 00:01:59,072
that stranger was...

23
00:01:59,073 --> 00:02:01,499
Yeah. It was Kim Jaehyun.

24
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:03,375
We crossed paths by chance,

25
00:02:03,376 --> 00:02:05,519
but I recognized him instantly.

26
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:06,919
And sure enough,

27
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:11,739
the people around Kim Jaehyun
started disappearing one by one.

28
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:14,661
If the same thing happens to you too...

29
00:02:17,380 --> 00:02:19,609
Don't worry

30
00:02:19,610 --> 00:02:23,586
I'm not letting Kim Jaehyun
hurt anyone ever again.

31
00:02:25,499 --> 00:02:28,181
Okay... I'll trust you.

32
00:02:52,959 --> 00:02:55,427
Isn't that Kim Yunghui over there?

33
00:02:55,428 --> 00:02:57,023
Huh?

34
00:02:57,024 --> 00:02:58,912
Ah...

35
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:02,389
Do you wanna head in first, hyung?

36
00:03:02,390 --> 00:03:05,545
I had something I wanted
to talk to Kim Yunghui about.

37
00:03:17,458 --> 00:03:19,766
Hyung!

38
00:03:19,767 --> 00:03:21,668
Oh, you're here.

39
00:03:23,116 --> 00:03:24,229
Where's Hyunjun?

40
00:03:24,230 --> 00:03:25,585
He went in first.

41
00:03:25,586 --> 00:03:27,586
Ah...

42
00:03:29,026 --> 00:03:32,778
Did you... think about yesterday?

43
00:03:33,597 --> 00:03:35,597
What?

44
00:03:35,832 --> 00:03:39,065
Can't you just take me instead?

45
00:03:41,100 --> 00:03:43,156
That's...

46
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,461
I like you.

47
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:50,710
So I want to help you.

48
00:03:57,224 --> 00:04:00,940
I don't expect you to feel
the same way about me

49
00:04:00,941 --> 00:04:03,739
I just want us to stay good friends.

50
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:05,565
That's all.

51
00:04:12,099 --> 00:04:14,688
I'm okay with that.

52
00:04:25,113 --> 00:04:26,866
You're back?

53
00:04:26,867 --> 00:04:28,867
Yeah.

54
00:04:37,971 --> 00:04:39,082
Hyung.

55
00:04:39,083 --> 00:04:40,313
Hm?

56
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:43,889
How do you think you'd
feel if I disappeared?

57
00:04:43,890 --> 00:04:46,001
What kind of question is that?

58
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:51,958
I was just curious.

59
00:04:55,137 --> 00:04:58,932
I'd go wherever you are.

60
00:05:13,862 --> 00:05:16,609
I'm not going anywhere.

61
00:05:24,792 --> 00:05:26,665
Hey!

62
00:05:30,820 --> 00:05:33,485
I need to talk to you.

63
00:05:33,486 --> 00:05:35,499
About what?

64
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:37,156
Not here.

65
00:05:49,389 --> 00:05:53,053
What, you trying to threaten me out here?

66
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:57,497
I'm staying here, just like you wanted.

67
00:06:02,460 --> 00:06:05,179
But let me ask you one thing.

68
00:06:05,180 --> 00:06:08,053
Do you seriously not feel any guilt...

69
00:06:08,054 --> 00:06:10,122
for what you've done to all those people?

70
00:06:14,575 --> 00:06:17,983
Wow, guilt?

71
00:06:17,984 --> 00:06:19,229
Why?

72
00:06:19,230 --> 00:06:22,081
You want me to feel bad or something?

73
00:06:22,561 --> 00:06:24,561
I see.

74
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:27,040
Got it.

75
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:30,457
You piece of shit.

76
00:06:31,732 --> 00:06:34,649
Wait... don't tell me.

77
00:06:34,650 --> 00:06:37,731
Guess you don't know the
underworld's biggest taboo.

78
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:42,799
I already lost my immortality.

79
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:45,798
The moment I fell in love
with a human, it was over.

80
00:06:45,799 --> 00:06:47,798
What?

81
00:06:47,799 --> 00:06:49,799
Oh, right.

82
00:06:50,339 --> 00:06:52,339
And one more thing.

83
00:06:52,945 --> 00:06:57,456
Did you know you were
wanted in the underworld?

84
00:06:58,092 --> 00:07:00,020
What the...

85
00:07:03,276 --> 00:07:04,765
[- Hyung, I think I found the infamous
fugitive - You found the fugitive?]

86
00:07:04,790 --> 00:07:07,003
[- Yeah, I'm sure of it... If I alter the
ledger and take him instead... what happens?]

87
00:07:07,053 --> 00:07:08,981
[The original ledger can't be
changed. Once your evidence is verified,

88
00:07:09,005 --> 00:07:10,713
we'll issue you a special warrant
ledger. Upload the evidence]

89
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:21,774
The one whose name
is written in this ledger...

90
00:07:21,775 --> 00:07:25,478
open the path to the
underworld this instant.

91
00:07:25,479 --> 00:07:27,794
How did you...

92
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:31,717
Your name has been
called, and your time is up.

93
00:07:31,718 --> 00:07:33,718
No...

94
00:07:35,371 --> 00:07:37,371
No!!

95
00:07:51,633 --> 00:07:54,607
[Yeomra]

96
00:07:57,868 --> 00:08:00,569
You who restored the
balance between life and death,

97
00:08:00,570 --> 00:08:03,929
you have earned the right
to return to the underworld.

98
00:08:03,930 --> 00:08:07,398
Come back home with me.

99
00:08:08,050 --> 00:08:11,639
I've fallen in love with a human

100
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:18,549
I want to grow old with him in
the human world and die by his side.

101
00:08:18,550 --> 00:08:21,169
And if I die here,

102
00:08:21,170 --> 00:08:23,909
I'll see you then.

103
00:08:23,910 --> 00:08:27,694
You foolish child. This
chance will never come again.

104
00:08:27,695 --> 00:08:31,757
And even if you regret this choice,
it can never be undone.

105
00:08:33,603 --> 00:08:37,831
I won't regret it.

106
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:10,700
"Fix the Error!"

